            <title>[HBASE-4780] Lower mini cluster shutdown time in HRegionServer#waitOnAllRegionsToClose and ServerManager#letRegionServersShutdown</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4780</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HRegionServer#waitOnAllRegionsToClose sleep 1s &lt;br/&gt;
 Lower waiting time&lt;br/&gt;
 benefits: around 0.8s at shutdown&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ServerManager.letRegionServersShutdown() waits 1 second =&amp;gt; responsible for 0.5 seconds in a HBase cluster stops&lt;br/&gt;
  Can be replaced by a notification&lt;br/&gt;
  Benefits: around 0.5s at shutdown&lt;/p&gt;</description>
